    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extra Bank Holiday when Covid restrictions are finally lifted",
        "additional_details": "This will go a small way to make up for all the gatherings that have not been able to happen for birthdays, Christmas and other celebrations during 2020.",
        "background": "When Covid restrictions are finally lifted across the country, put in place a bank holiday (Monday or Friday) to make a three day weekend, giving family and friends the opportunity to celebrate together.",
